{"tid":1433940,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"引導屋企民意的必勝法","createTime":"2019-08-08T15:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T17:13:52.000Z","uid":236778,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"963ea058e9e043925f962414c8ae2b5c91f8115c","tid":1433940,"uid":236778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:32:04.000Z","msg":"今日同藍絲屋企人又傾不合作運動。老母話示威者破壞經濟，所以佢可能會轉唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。(明明都係貿易戰影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)由於我之前已經又攞證據又冷靜討論都無用，所以我今次決定<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">改變策略，因勢利導</span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 班示威者又搞搞陣，又搞稅局，又搞差經濟，我遲啲想轉工加人工養你地都無機會啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咪就係，宜家已經無人控制到啲示威者</span></strong>，警察又失晒控特首控制唔到。你要<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">嚇走同說服五萬個、十萬個示威者唔好不合作係無可能咖</span></strong>，佢地不合作一定會有排搞。反而有個方法就易好多令到示威者唔再出黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 講黎聽下？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">出黎遊行，向林鄭施壓</span></strong>，希望佢快啲滿足示威者，咁咪無人會再阻住你去稅局囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 又好似係。。。(隔咗一隔之後就問我幾時會有和平集會)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因勢利導！</span></strong>呢招對指責示威者破壞社會、經濟嘅人特別有用。目的就係要以佢嘅出發點黎提出一個佢會覺得可行嘅方法，再將佢引導落我地想佢做嘅野(遊行，收集民意)。<br />\n可能你會話佢地都唔係真係支持民主，支持未威者，但係我會話你想改變一個人嘅思維係好難，反而順住佢嘅思維再去說服佢就易好多，大家嘅衝突都無咁多。你都知港豬最驚紛爭。如果大家試過晒勸佢、down 立場app等方法都改變唔到，不彷試下呢個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">result-oriented</span></strong>嘅做法，因勢利導！"},{"pid":"677e1ec3242be0a1dcd3ef9a594dd5225de4aa16","tid":1433940,"uid":236778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:32:16.000Z","msg":"push pish"},{"pid":"519c322b50e05faea9776dfd0ae6b95723e1339c","tid":1433940,"uid":236778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"677e1ec3242be0a1dcd3ef9a594dd5225de4aa16","tid":1433940,"uid":236778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:32:16.000Z","msg":"push pish"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:32:43.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山"},{"pid":"97095e0b62800d21a862925823eaa0b7f3d2fff1","tid":1433940,"uid":236778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:32:55.000Z","msg":"咩都要試"},{"pid":"1e865d5182188e1e1b42dc8e2aab3fa1a681a510","tid":1433940,"uid":236778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:35:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"40c8dae27a386654bdccb689e2fd0f19b0bdc2e0","tid":1433940,"uid":236778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:36:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"10fc3d58f749562cf5957ba0e136a80e7c374b11","tid":1433940,"uid":236778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:36:35.000Z","msg":"pushhhhgg"},{"pid":"70f873e23cea304ab71bd879ed86805920c0f381","tid":1433940,"uid":236778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"yoyoyo老母well done"},{"pid":"4814930e5e808fc0cbaca2012fc56f6ad3d39a35","tid":1433940,"uid":236778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:37:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d264e76ecbfc90b60a3203da2ba9bf6d1ba2a07b","tid":1433940,"uid":236778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:37:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5d1eb9a50934c8e1d8ec08e19cb13128df3d8b21","tid":1433940,"uid":236778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:39:27.000Z